It's working fine for me on Windows 7 Home Premium 64 bit. For everybody that's having problems with the gauges, all you've got to do is start the gauges up. If you go to the 'Super 80 Professional Center', 'Training', and 'Tips & Tricks', then click on 'How to power up the aircraft/cockpit' it'll show you how to start up the gauges.
